<h1>Library terms and condition</h1>
<h2>General conditions</h2>
<ul>
    <li>All members and users of the City Library are required to sign in and out on arrival and departure</li>
    <li>No mobile phones</li>
    <li>All visitors are required to create account and provide all required documents</li>
</ul>
<h2>Borrowing conditions</h2>
<li>One member can borrow books for a four-week loan period</li>
<li>Book can be renewed for another loan period of four weeks</li>
<li>It is the borrower's responsibility to ensure that items are return to the City Library on time</li>
<li>Only the registered member can borrow a book. A daily visitor only can check the book on site.</li>
<h2>Renewal conditions</h2>
<li>Borrowed items must be returned or renewed on the due date</li>
<li>Renewals may be made in person or by application</li>
<li>Items not renewed or returned to the City Library after 3 reminder email notices have been issued
    (without an explanation from the borrower) will be deemed to have been lost by the borrower and will be charged.</li>


